
# ASP.NET Core Choice Points

## Middleware Choices

The two middlewares are not compatible. 

* ASP.NET Core Middleware (not equal to Katana Middleware)
* OWIN Middleware

## Runtime Choices

* DNX CLR
* DNX Mono
* DNX CoreCLR

## .NET Choices

* Full Framework
  * .NET Framework 
  * Mono (open-source, cross-platform port of the Full Framework)
* .NET Core

## Operating System Choices

* Windows
* Ubuntu
* Debian
* CentOS
* Fedora
* Mac
* Docker

## Hosting Choices

* IIS
* ASP.NET Host (`Microsoft.AspNet.Server.Kestrel`)
* OWIN Host (e.g. 

## Server Choices

* IIS
* Kestrel (behind IIS or NGINX)

## Dev Tooling Choices

* Command Line Interface with a text editor (Vim, Sublime, VS Code...)
* Visual Studio 2015 Community